<item>
            <title>[SOLR-12192] Error when ulimit is unlimited</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12192</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;solr@fd8031538f4b:/opt/solr$  ulimit -u
unlimited

solr@fd8031538f4b:/opt/solr$  bin/solr
/opt/solr/bin/solr: line 1452: [: unlimited: integer expression expected
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The solr start script should check for &quot;unlimited&quot; and not print that error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch on &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/pull/352&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/lucene-solr/pull/352&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
